{"tid":1492683,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"人民日報：要止暴制亂　不要指望中央會在原則問題讓步","createTime":"2019-08-21T02:48:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T05:48:32.000Z","uid":161863,"like":31,"dislike":116,"uniUserReply":113,"replies":[{"pid":"15f43d0528d78b62974a1ac96969348f4a8045c3","tid":1492683,"uid":161863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T02:48:54.000Z","msg":"《人民日報海外版》發表評論員文章，認為香港局勢要出現轉機，不能靠向反對派妥協退讓，也不要指望中央會在原則問題上讓步。 文章說，香港局勢依舊危險、嚴峻，當務之急和壓倒一切的任務，就是止暴制亂、恢復秩序。香港局勢要出現轉機，要靠特區警隊和執法司法機關嚴正執法、公正司法；要靠愛國愛港陣營團結一致、堅決鬥爭；要靠廣大港人積極行動起來，敢於向暴力說不，向踐踏法治的行為說不，以正壓邪。 文章又說，香港反對派和激進勢力切勿誤判形勢，把克制當軟弱，切勿低估中央政府和全國人民捍衛國家主權、安全、統一，維護香港繁榮穩定的堅強意志和堅定決心。<br />\n<br />\nSource: RTHK <a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1475856-20190821.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1475856-20190821.htm&d=DXuv2gayA%2Byyjyt3RGK41Ou9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=1e3b2761\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1475856-20190821.htm&h=d20f61ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1475856-20190821.htm</a>"},{"pid":"633f7f9d3922bece5dd47c4faa51868b2ca4ef63","tid":1492683,"uid":183758,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T02:49:36.000Z","msg":"收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97b7fedc364a56c1290646db5a5d9aff65220f78","tid":1492683,"uid":269533,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T02:49:44.000Z","msg":"攬炒"},{"pid":"1aa56bd9747ec4b3ec7bc86277cd6406d3f9ebaf","tid":1492683,"uid":183758,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T02:50:09.000Z","msg":"堅決鬥爭<br />\n<br />\n文革"},{"pid":"b60288ab5b8df53d2c745dc47a4a3e1968ab6506","tid":1492683,"uid":31200,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T02:50:23.000Z","msg":"大家咁話<img src=\"/